Write a program to capitalize the alternate words in a sentence.

a=input().split(" ")
for i in range(len(a)):
    if i%2==0: 
        print(a[i].upper(),end=" ")
    else:
        print(a[i],end=" ")

Input1:
Better late than never

Output1:
BETTER late THAN never

Input2:
The early bird catches the worm

Output2:
THE early BIRD catches THE worm
